                  <entry>
                     <p>kogito.logger.always-include</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>
                     <p>Always include the Workflow debug logger.
By default, this will only be included in dev and test.
Setting this to true will also include the Workflow debug logger in Prod</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>
                     <p>boolean</p>
